write a JavaScript program to generate and print out the ascii character and hexadecimal codes for 0 to 7f
Here's a JavaScript program that generates ASCII characters and their corresponding Hexadecimal codes from 0 to F (15 decimal). The output will be printed in console.
```javascript
for (let i = 0; i <= 0xF; ++i) {
    const asciiChar = String.fromCharCode(i);
    const hexValue = i.toString(16).toUpperCase();

    console.log(`ASCII Character: ${asciiChar}`);
    console.log(`Hexadecimal Code: ${hexValue}`);
}
```
